headline: 2 Financials Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Ignore
summary: Financial providers use their expertise in capital allocation and risk assessment to help facilitate economic growth while offering consumers and businesses essential financial services. But uncertainty about fiscal and monetary policy has tempered enthusiasm, and over the past six months, the industry has pulled back by 6.5%. This drawdown is a stark contrast from the S&P 500’s 7.2% gain.
